No pathotype differences were found between 2010 and 2011.
[$Cucumis melo#Plant*] cultigen MR-1 was less susceptible to Michigan [$P.cubensis #Virus*]populations than other [$C.melo#Plant*] cultigens.
No symptoms or signs of [$infe#Method*]ction were detected on cultigens of [@Cucurbita moschata#Plant*] and [$C.pepo#Plant*].
